{"type": "article", "id": 6253, "title": "投影寻真 Shadowmatic", "description": null, "date": "1970-01-01T00:00:00Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": null, "column": null, "author": 3603, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 1, "image": "img/default_images/missing_article.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;padding:0px;color:#737373;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"color:#737373;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;\">年后没几天就是元宵节，元宵节中赏灯可是中华民族的传统风俗。有灯也就有了影子，有了影子也就有了手影等游戏的出现。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;padding:0px;color:#737373;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"color:#737373;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604213616Mg5EKIDv8Hm0TUfc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;padding:0px;color:#737373;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/shadowmatic/id775888026?mt=8&amp;ign-mpt=uo%3D4\" target=\"_blank\">《投影寻真》</a>这款游戏就类似于手影，不过把手换成了在空气中悬浮的小物件。玩家要做的就是调整这些不规则小物件的方向，直到在墙面上留下有意义的图像，从动物到工具等等都有可能是谜底。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;padding:0px;color:#737373;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t在元宵节没赶上假期的 2015 年，在游戏里与灯光做做游戏，多少可以弥补点对于花灯回忆的渴望吧。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;padding:0px;color:#737373;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"color:#000000;\">更详细的介绍请戳</span><a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/display/articles/5533.html\" style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;color:#0069D6;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">这里</span></a><span style=\"color:#000000;\">。</span> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}